00:11:37,410 --> 00:11:57,270
whether it's on this mailer or we agreed to do a second mailer, the calculator to what it would cost a resident per household should either be in a QR code and lead to that place on the website so that people can start calculating, you know,

176
00:11:57,677 --> 00:11:59,778
