179
00:12:07,843 --> 00:12:11,165
We kind of know what the total estimated project costs are.

180
00:12:11,686 --> 00:12:15,248
I think our OPM and designer could figure out the bottom line.

181
00:12:15,308 --> 00:12:17,389
I did a back of the envelope calculation.

182
00:12:17,409 --> 00:12:23,993
And I think we just need to make sure that that is linked somewhere on the website through this postcard.

183
00:12:25,698 --> 00:12:40,062
I think it's far too early for us to be using numbers that are A, not informed by any information directly from the MSBA and B, not reflective of any of the work that the city needs to do to determine like how this will be paid for.

184
00:12:40,622 --> 00:12:50,345
So I think that number would be fairly alarmist at this point where what I'm trying to do is make sure that the people who want to know about this project and want to be involved in it can do that.

185
00:12:51,185 --> 00:12:53,726
Whether we decide to send something out down the line

186
00:12:54,525 --> 00:12:55,606
is a different question.

187
00:12:55,646 --> 00:13:04,669
And we may, we may well want to do that as well, but we, I would not support sending a tax calculator out at this point in time.

188
00:13:04,849 --> 00:13:06,530
We don't know the total project costs.

189
00:13:07,050 --> 00:13:09,191
We don't know what the MSBA will cost share for.

190
00:13:09,251 --> 00:13:13,453
We don't know how the city can support this project without pushing it on taxpayers.

191
00:13:13,473 --> 00:13:17,855
Like we don't know any of the things that would be important to be able to create an accurate calculator.

192
00:13:19,443 --> 00:13:21,464
So what would be the message of the mail?

193
00:13:21,865 --> 00:13:24,186
You said awareness, but we've been at it for two years.

194
00:13:24,866 --> 00:13:31,510
Everyone I talk to asks me about the high school and say, everyone in the city knows that we're thinking about a new high school.

195
00:13:32,111 --> 00:13:36,453
So like, maybe that's false, but that's my perception.

196
00:13:37,414 --> 00:13:42,737
And so, you know, the messaging, the literal words that go on the postcard are important.

197
00:13:43,097 --> 00:13:47,400
You don't want to mislead anybody and we should have a purpose for the mail.

198
00:13:48,430 --> 00:13:52,172
If it's only awareness, then that's going to lead to limited wording.

199
00:13:52,953 --> 00:13:56,895
If it's come on out and get involved, then that's different wording.

200
00:13:56,935 --> 00:14:03,559
It's going to have specific information for people to contact or otherwise get involved.

201
00:14:04,479 --> 00:14:08,922
Will we have a chance to discuss the words that go on mailer before it goes out?

202
00:14:11,984 --> 00:14:12,684
