217
00:15:34,204 --> 00:15:41,206
So I think people are aware of what is happening, but I don't know if they understand the depth of what's involved in this project.

218
00:15:42,867 --> 00:15:44,087
That's awesome.

219
00:15:46,809 --> 00:15:48,230
don't agree that everybody knows.

220
00:15:48,490 --> 00:16:03,577
And my only feeling for why that can't be true is that literally a butter to the library claim to have no idea what construction, which to me says, some people are working hard to not know it almost.

221
00:16:03,757 --> 00:16:06,078
I mean, that example still blows me away.

222
00:16:06,118 --> 00:16:06,978
Because the library.

223
00:16:07,418 --> 00:16:07,658
Yeah.

224
00:16:07,899 --> 00:16:13,041
But you're literally against the library and you said you didn't know until it was being demolished.

225
00:16:14,341 --> 00:16:15,302
I mean, that was,

226
00:16:16,168 --> 00:16:20,370
That was a wake up call to me that they're going to be good to not know until it's done.

227
00:16:20,690 --> 00:16:23,692
Like they're going to be like driving by and be like, Oh, I guess we're going to do that.

228
00:16:24,312 --> 00:16:30,596
So I think we need to get everybody Nicole.

229
00:16:30,816 --> 00:16:31,616
