235
00:16:51,805 --> 00:16:54,025
But even if they're involved in like MFN too, they don't know what goes on.

236
00:16:54,046 --> 00:16:59,408
So I think really covering the comprehensive aspect, I think it's really important, particularly at this point.

237
00:17:00,408 --> 00:17:02,209
