You have one access in, one access out, and you're going to try to widen that access.

983
01:22:54,313 --> 01:23:03,075
You can work with the synagogue or other means, but the farther you push it back as a parent, those kids are going to say, hey dad, can you drive me?

984
01:23:03,275 --> 01:23:05,016
I'm going to be dad, they're going to drive them every day.

985
01:23:05,530 --> 01:23:12,296
