1019
01:26:16,354 --> 01:26:20,735
This is a building for the next 50 to 80 years for educating our children.

1020
01:26:21,115 --> 01:26:26,476
And I think that's really, really important to remember because education changes over 10, 20, 30, 50 years.

1021
01:26:29,297 --> 01:26:34,820
So having spaces built that can be used and flexed differently is super important.

1022
01:26:35,781 --> 01:26:42,384
It's actually fascinating to me how vocational education is really back heavily and core.

1023
01:26:43,305 --> 01:26:49,868
And that is something that has done like a 50-year turnaround that has changed so dramatically.

1024
01:26:50,068 --> 01:26:51,149
